{"type": "article", "id": 5287, "title": "Lightmark 书签", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-16T08:00:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233613rTkoQnpBNdsulULD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自以色列的 Peleg Design 工作室鳝鱼赋予日常生活中的普通事物以新鲜且有创意性的解读，比如这款最新推出的书签 Lightmark ，就是将一款小型阅读灯的轮廓复制简化，运用在了书签上。设计团队希望这枚小小的书签能够点亮你最后阅读的那一页，它如同一盏微型台灯，插入书页的黄色书签部分有如一束直射下来的光束。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233611i46peGFRLVsf2QWo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233611CPK5p1efUXdLjzwA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233611aoQlCFxdPOGZUJfn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233612NsGOC7Y3wuJk5Dg9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}